text: Cutlers Ait is an island in the River Thames in England adjacent to Romney Island and Romney Lock, near Windsor, Berkshire. The island is a tree-covered strip adjacent to the opposite bank of the river from the Lock, near Eton. Romney weir sits between the two islands. ==See also== *Islands in the River Thames Category:Islands of Berkshire Category:Islands of the River Thames
